# Visual Design System

## Colors
- **Navy** `#1A2B4C` — Headers, primary buttons, price boxes, dark panels, active states
- **Navy hover** `#253A66` — Button hover state
- **Gold** `#E5C37A` — CTAs, highlights, labels on dark backgrounds, accents
- **Red** `#D10024` — Discount badges, sale prices
- **Background** `#f8fafc` (slate-50) — Page backgrounds, list items
- **White** `#ffffff` — Card backgrounds, inputs
- **Slate** `#f8f9fa` — Cart page background

## Typography
- All text in Vietnamese (no English labels in UI)
- `font-black` — Headings, prices, CTAs, labels
- `font-bold` — Body text, descriptions
- `uppercase tracking-widest` or `tracking-tighter` — Headings and labels
- `text-[10px]` — Small labels and badges
- `rounded-2xl` or `rounded-3xl` — Cards and panels

## Buttons
- Primary: `bg-[#1A2B4C] text-[#E5C37A]` with `shadow-xl shadow-[#1A2B4C]/20`
- Secondary: `bg-white border-2 border-[#1A2B4C] text-[#1A2B4C]`
- Danger: `bg-[#D10024] text-white`
- Height: `h-14` or `h-16`, `rounded-2xl`
- Text: `font-black uppercase text-xs tracking-widest`

## Cards
- `rounded-2xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm border border-slate-100`
- Hover: `hover:shadow-md transition-shadow`
- Dark variant: `rounded-[2rem] bg-[#1A2B4C] p-8 text-white shadow-2xl border border-[#E5C37A]/20`

## Responsive
- Mobile first: default styles = mobile, `lg:` = desktop
- Mobile breakpoint: 390px (smallest supported)
- Bottom padding on mobile pages: `pb-32` (accounts for fixed bottom nav)
- Sticky mobile actions: above `bottom-16` (bottom nav height)
